WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.869
Good morning, family. I have another

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:05.670
video for you all. I have some things

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:08.230
I want to say.

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.790
I'm a watchman, and the Lord shows

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:14.110
me a lot of things. A lot of things

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:18.070
he shows me are very heavy.

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:20.509
He gives this

00:00:20.519 --> 00:00:22.630
stuff to me when I'm praying and says,

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:24.710
'Hey, Brandon, heads up. This is what's

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:27.390
coming down the road here.'There

00:00:27.390 --> 00:00:27.400
are

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.029
some things we can

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:31.870
avoid and some things we can't.

00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:35.150
Like I said,

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:36.389
I'm always trying to

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:39.549
figure out... I know we have power and

00:00:39.559 --> 00:00:42.830
authority as believers. We're seated with

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:46.310
Him in the heavenlies, and I know that

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:49.990
when we join together as a

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.470
group and we pray, I tell you all

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:56.830
the plan of the enemy.

00:00:56.840 --> 00:00:58.910
I'm blowing my trumpet. I'm a watchman

00:00:58.920 --> 00:01:00.910
on the wall saying, 'Listen,

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:03.670
the bozo devil is going to try to do

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:07.109
this. Let's stop it.'I know

00:01:07.119 --> 00:01:10.670
the Lord's trying to warn you

00:01:10.670 --> 00:01:10.680
all,

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.270
warn the world,

00:01:12.270 --> 00:01:12.280
and

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:15.149
warn America. I thought this was

00:01:15.159 --> 00:01:16.590
interesting: he made a statement to me while I

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.910
was out taking care of my dogs.

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:20.910
He said,

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:25.190
'Brandon, if Abraham's intercession for

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:26.789
Sodom and Gomorrah—when he was praying,

00:01:26.799 --> 00:01:30.109
he said, Lord, if there be

00:01:31.870 --> 00:01:31.880
ten

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:37.389
righteous, would you spare the city? And

00:01:37.399 --> 00:01:40.310
he said back to Abraham, Yes, I'd be

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:44.709
willing to spare the city for ten

00:01:44.709 --> 00:01:44.719
righteous.'I

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:47.069
believe if he

00:01:47.079 --> 00:01:48.990
would have taken it down a step

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.789
further... because I know he

00:01:51.799 --> 00:01:53.469
thought in his mind there has to be

00:01:53.469 --> 00:01:53.479
ten

00:01:53.479 --> 00:01:56.389
righteous people standing in

00:01:56.399 --> 00:01:58.230
behalf of Sodom and Gomorrah. They

00:01:58.240 --> 00:02:00.389
were a very

00:02:00.399 --> 00:02:02.429
immoral

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:05.230
city, of course, and it was wiped

00:02:05.240 --> 00:02:08.109
off the face of the earth.

00:02:08.119 --> 00:02:11.670
He was interceding for them and he

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:13.470
said,

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:16.670
'Brandon, if I was willing to do that for

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:20.229
them back then under the Old

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:22.030
Covenant without

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:26.790
Jesus, how

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:30.750
much more with you interceding now would

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:32.309
I do it for

00:02:32.309 --> 00:02:32.319
you?'He

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:36.910
said, 'I called you on YouTube to

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:42.070
tell my people what's coming, not for a

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:45.990
lot of it to come.'I believe

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:48.470
with our group of intercessory prayer

00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:52.030
people, we are able to do a lot of damage

00:02:52.040 --> 00:02:55.710
to the kingdom of darkness.

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:58.509
I warned you all about the water

00:02:58.519 --> 00:03:01.430
attack, about the men

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:03.030
trying to pour stuff into the lakes

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:05.949
and mess with our water. I believe we

00:03:05.959 --> 00:03:09.509
can stop that.

00:03:09.519 --> 00:03:12.110
Whenever he

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.670
came to me and said that,

00:03:13.670 --> 00:03:13.680
it

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:15.509
was just out of the

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:17.229
clear blue. I was

00:03:17.239 --> 00:03:19.270
cleaning up dog feces,

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:21.830
doing my normal thing

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:24.070
with my puppies, and when he said that to

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:25.630
me, I was like, 'Wow,

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:26.710
Lord, where does this come

00:03:26.710 --> 00:03:26.720
from?'I

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:28.949
wasn't even really praying; I'm always in

00:03:28.959 --> 00:03:31.470
the state of prayer in my heart,

00:03:31.480 --> 00:03:33.670
always just talking and

00:03:33.670 --> 00:03:33.680
having

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:36.030
communion with the Father.

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:39.949
He knows I'm always willing to

00:03:39.959 --> 00:03:41.990
jump in that river and pray with Him.

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:47.910
It

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:50.229
is always a flow. The more you

00:03:50.239 --> 00:03:52.030
build that, the more you'll flow with the

00:03:52.040 --> 00:03:53.869
Holy Spirit. This was not a

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:56.830
real supernatural moment; it

00:03:56.830 --> 00:03:56.840
was

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:59.390
just a normal day, spraying off

00:03:59.390 --> 00:03:59.400
the

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:01.030
grass and

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:04.149
cleaning up the yard, and he just said

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:07.110
that to me. It hit me hard.

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:11.270
He said, 'Remember, Brandon: If My people

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:14.190
who are called by My name would

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:16.189
humble themselves and

00:04:16.199 --> 00:04:20.069
pray and turn from their wicked

00:04:20.069 --> 00:04:20.079
ways...'Then

00:04:20.079 --> 00:04:22.710
he stopped and said to me,

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:27.710
'I did not say if the

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:30.070
world would humble

00:04:30.070 --> 00:04:30.080
themselves

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:32.909
and pray. I didn't say the world.

00:04:32.919 --> 00:04:35.230
I didn't say Joe Biden. I didn't say

00:04:35.240 --> 00:04:39.029
Nancy Pelosi. I said, My

00:04:39.029 --> 00:04:39.039
people.'He's

00:04:39.039 --> 00:04:41.749
talking about you and me,

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:43.070
people who are on

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:48.510
fire for Him. If we would humble ourselves and

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:51.390
pray, we would hear from heaven

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:53.950
and He would heal our land. He would

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:56.629
deliver us from what's going on

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:58.830
and

00:04:58.840 --> 00:05:01.029
do what

00:05:01.029 --> 00:05:01.039
needs

00:05:01.039 --> 00:05:02.469
to be done to help turn around the

00:05:02.479 --> 00:05:04.909
nation. If we have a group of people—maybe

00:05:04.909 --> 00:05:04.919
I

00:05:04.919 --> 00:05:07.430
have a

00:05:07.430 --> 00:05:07.440
10,000-strong

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:10.909
group of

00:05:10.919 --> 00:05:13.710
believers on here worldwide—I know we can

00:05:13.710 --> 00:05:13.720
do something big.

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:16.550
Some of my prayer videos get a

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:17.830
couple thousand people

00:05:17.830 --> 00:05:17.840
who

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:18.790
watch the whole thing. I know

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.029
you're interceding with me the whole

00:05:20.039 --> 00:05:22.430
time.

00:05:22.430 --> 00:05:22.440
I

00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:25.070
just want to encourage

00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:28.469
you all that this is not a 'sky is

00:05:28.469 --> 00:05:28.479
falling'time.

00:05:28.479 --> 00:05:31.629
I told you all

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:33.430
when I went to the throne, he

00:05:33.440 --> 00:05:37.390
said to me, 'Brandon, I never

00:05:37.390 --> 00:05:37.400
designed

00:05:37.400 --> 00:05:40.309
the armor for

00:05:40.319 --> 00:05:43.230
retreat. I designed the armor to take

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:45.870
dominion and authority, and take back

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:48.390
what the devil's tried to

00:05:48.390 --> 00:05:48.400
steal.'It's

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:51.110
marching forward,

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:53.909
taking action, taking

00:05:53.919 --> 00:05:55.909
that sword of the spirit, the

00:05:55.919 --> 00:05:58.749
shield of faith, and the helmet of salvation

00:05:58.759 --> 00:06:01.270
and smacking that

00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:04.150
devil in the head. It's not to run

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:06.390
away because there's no armor for the

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:10.110
backside. The Lord said this to me:

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:17.629
'Brandon, the devil is the Lord of the

00:06:17.639 --> 00:06:22.390
Flies. He is like

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:24.589
a fly.'That's

00:06:24.589 --> 00:06:24.599
how

00:06:24.599 --> 00:06:25.749
the Lord showed

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:28.710
me. He said, 'Do you know how you get

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:30.870
the devil not to bother you so

00:06:30.870 --> 00:06:30.880
much?'I

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:36.230
said, 'How, Lord?'He said, 'Get hot.

00:06:36.240 --> 00:06:42.270
Get extremely on fire for Me. For a

00:06:42.280 --> 00:06:46.309
fly does not land on a

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:50.430
flame or a very hot

00:06:50.430 --> 00:06:50.440
surface.'He

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:53.390
said the hotter you get

00:06:53.400 --> 00:06:59.670
with Me, the less a fly can land.

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:03.150
He said they land on

00:07:03.150 --> 00:07:03.160
the

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:07.150
lukewarm when they smell food

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:11.150
or they smell poo.

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:14.309
Flies do, but they will not land on

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:15.830
something that's on

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:19.710
fire. He said the devil is like a fly,

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:23.029
and the more you become on fire for Me,

00:07:23.039 --> 00:07:25.189
the less that devil's going to try to

00:07:25.199 --> 00:07:27.390
mess with you because he's a fly and he

00:07:27.390 --> 00:07:27.400
doesn't

00:07:27.400 --> 00:07:29.589
want to touch a hot surface

00:07:29.599 --> 00:07:33.150
because he'll get burnt. That's what

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:35.350
I'm trying to tell you all. Get on

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:37.390
fire for Jesus. How do

00:07:37.400 --> 00:07:38.510
you get on fire?

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:45.550
Spend time with Him

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:49.830
daily. Get before Him, get on your knees,

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:53.550
and worship the Father. Read His Bible,

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:56.869
pray, spend time with Him in worship.

00:07:56.879 --> 00:08:00.270
Worship Him in singing and in praying,

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:03.230
and you'll get on fire for Jesus.

00:08:03.240 --> 00:08:07.189
Faith comes by hearing and

00:08:07.199 --> 00:08:10.309
hearing by the word of God. Get that word

00:08:10.319 --> 00:08:12.670
down inside of you. I'm telling you,

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:14.670
that fire is going to be like a

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:17.230
furnace. You keep putting coals and gas

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:18.510
in it,

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:21.550
and that devil's going to run.

00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:22.830
He doesn't want to get

00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:25.070
around that fire. He'll

00:08:25.080 --> 00:08:26.510
be like that little

00:08:26.520 --> 00:08:28.710
fly: you touch the

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:32.909
flame, you burn him up.

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:34.589
That's the way the Lord showed

00:08:34.599 --> 00:08:36.909
me. I started dealing with

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.829
stuff and he goes, 'Brandon, you're getting

00:08:38.839 --> 00:08:41.750
lukewarm. Son,

00:08:41.750 --> 00:08:41.760
you've

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:43.230
got to come back under that fire

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:48.150
and fan that

00:08:48.150 --> 00:08:48.160
flame.'I

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:51.110
heard somebody preaching this last

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:52.470
Wednesday about authority

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:55.230
in your realm of authority. I believe we

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:59.949
have power and authority over storms.

00:08:59.959 --> 00:09:02.389
I take it all the time. We

00:09:02.399 --> 00:09:04.150
pray over our storms, we take communion,

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:07.269
we tell the storm to

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:11.150
die like Jesus did: 'Peace, be

00:09:11.150 --> 00:09:11.160
still.'You

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:12.990
can call the storm; you're not going

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:14.750
to hail on my property. You're not going

00:09:14.760 --> 00:09:16.269
to have strong winds; we're not going to

00:09:16.279 --> 00:09:18.069
lose power; we're not going to have any

00:09:18.079 --> 00:09:20.870
damage to our houses or trees.

00:09:20.880 --> 00:09:24.069
Satan, I bind you and I tell you now, you

00:09:24.079 --> 00:09:26.310
get out of here and you leave my stuff

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:29.430
alone. We have authority over you and we

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.389
have authority over the weather. I

00:09:31.399 --> 00:09:34.069
command this weather to be peace and be

00:09:34.079 --> 00:09:37.710
still over my area in the name of Jesus.

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:40.750
I command any tornadoes to go away

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:43.350
now. Go back up in that cloud and

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:46.230
stop it. That's just the way we talk to

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:49.150
them. My mom, my dad, my

00:09:49.150 --> 00:09:49.160
wife—we

00:09:49.160 --> 00:09:51.509
all talk

00:09:51.509 --> 00:09:51.519
to

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:54.670
the

00:09:54.670 --> 00:09:54.680
storms.

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:56.710
That's how we believe

00:09:56.710 --> 00:09:56.720
and

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:58.990
operate in the realm of

00:09:59.000 --> 00:09:59.910
the spirit.

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:03.550
We take authority over the storms.

00:10:03.550 --> 00:10:03.560
I

00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:06.150
had a lady asking

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.670
for rain for a certain area in Texas

00:10:08.670 --> 00:10:08.680
where

00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:11.350
they didn't have any. I

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:14.910
told her I'd stand with her for rain.

00:10:14.920 --> 00:10:17.590
She emailed back

00:10:17.590 --> 00:10:17.600
with

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.990
a picture showing all the

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:24.230
rain like a river.

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:29.670
I did what I said I'd do.

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:33.949
I started speaking the rain. I told

00:10:33.949 --> 00:10:33.959
it

00:10:33.959 --> 00:10:37.870
to come forth over Houston, interceding

00:10:37.880 --> 00:10:41.190
for Houston and The Woodlands, Texas. I started speaking to that rain, and now they have rivers and moats of rain everywhere. Not only can we stop the

00:10:41.190 --> 00:10:41.200
rain, but we can cause the rain to

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:42.750
come forth because

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:48.150
we

00:10:54.030 --> 00:10:54.040
have

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:01.990
authority over it. I call rain in

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:03.509
all the time. It starts getting dry and

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:05.310
they say, 'The drought

00:11:05.310 --> 00:11:05.320
monitor

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:09.389
is getting bad again and there's

00:11:09.399 --> 00:11:11.829
going to be no rain; lakes are drying

00:11:11.829 --> 00:11:11.839
up.'No.

00:11:11.839 --> 00:11:16.110
Rain, I call you forth in

00:11:16.120 --> 00:11:20.269
the name of Jesus. I say, 'Rain,

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:23.629
come from the north, south, east,

00:11:23.629 --> 00:11:23.639
and

00:11:23.639 --> 00:11:26.550
west. You will not have drought

00:11:26.560 --> 00:11:30.310
over this area.'I call that rain in.

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:35.030
Rain, come forth. I speak

00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:35.040
low-pressure

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:37.790
systems to come in for the

00:11:37.790 --> 00:11:37.800
Gulf

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:41.190
moisture to come up, or wherever the jet stream

00:11:41.190 --> 00:11:41.200
comes

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:44.310
over. I call forth

00:11:44.310 --> 00:11:44.320
four

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:46.629
inches

00:11:46.639 --> 00:11:49.470
of rain over

00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:51.750
the next

00:11:51.760 --> 00:11:54.750
week or two. I thank you,

00:11:54.760 --> 00:11:56.509
Father, that You're the Lord of the

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:59.670
harvest and You will bring rain for my

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:02.629
crops, the trees,

00:12:02.629 --> 00:12:02.639
and

00:12:02.639 --> 00:12:04.829
the grass.

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:10.230
You have to use your authority in these

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:13.470
last days more than ever before.

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:22.509
When you hear the weatherman say

00:12:22.519 --> 00:12:24.949
there's a storm coming,

00:12:24.959 --> 00:12:28.870
you say, 'Not my house,

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:32.189
not my area, not where I

00:12:35.079 --> 00:12:36.790
tread.'You've

00:12:40.600 --> 00:12:43.430
got to learn how to be bold about it, not

00:12:43.430 --> 00:12:43.440
shrinking

00:12:43.440 --> 00:12:45.870
back saying,

00:12:47.199 --> 00:12:50.949
'He won't protect me.'No, He's a

00:12:50.959 --> 00:12:53.829
good God; He's no respecter of persons.

00:12:55.880 --> 00:12:58.509
You have power and authority

00:12:58.519 --> 00:12:59.710
over the weather

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:01.230
and

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:03.069
your city. You pray over the

00:13:03.079 --> 00:13:05.110
city for your police officers

00:13:05.110 --> 00:13:05.120
and

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:08.430
churches.

00:13:08.440 --> 00:13:11.350
The authority of the believer works.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:17.069
At the name of

00:13:17.079 --> 00:13:20.230
Jesus, every knee will bow and every

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:24.110
tongue will confess that He is Lord.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:26.350
That's the kind of

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:28.629
power we have in Him.

00:13:34.120 --> 00:13:36.670
If there be

00:13:36.670 --> 00:13:36.680
ten

00:13:36.680 --> 00:13:39.790
righteous, He'd spare the city. How much

00:13:39.800 --> 00:13:42.590
more would He be willing to spare

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:47.750
America or delay things to

00:13:47.750 --> 00:13:47.760
allow

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:51.470
the harvest of souls?

00:13:51.480 --> 00:13:54.269
Why

00:13:54.269 --> 00:13:54.279
has

00:13:54.279 --> 00:13:56.790
He not come back yet?

00:13:56.800 --> 00:14:00.710
Because He is a God of mercy and

00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:06.269
He wants more harvest.

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:11.910
He sent His only begotten son to die for

00:14:11.920 --> 00:14:15.470
you. He doesn't want anybody to perish,

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:17.430
but for all to come to repentance.

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:20.150
Why

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:23.949
hasn't

00:14:23.959 --> 00:14:25.430
the Rapture

00:14:25.430 --> 00:14:25.440
happened?

00:14:25.440 --> 00:14:27.910
Because He's looking for

00:14:27.910 --> 00:14:27.920
the

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:30.389
harvest that matters most to Him. Gold, diamonds, and jewels—that's what He

00:14:32.639 --> 00:14:35.670
uses

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:44.749
for pavement.

00:14:44.759 --> 00:14:47.069
He

00:14:47.079 --> 00:14:49.269
doesn't

00:14:49.279 --> 00:14:52.430
care about gold;

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:55.189
it's asphalt to

00:14:55.199 --> 00:14:58.310
Him. What's important to Him is the heart

00:14:58.320 --> 00:14:59.670
of a man.

00:14:59.670 --> 00:14:59.680
It's

00:14:59.680 --> 00:15:02.230
important to Him that your loved

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:03.430
ones are

00:15:05.639 --> 00:15:08.150
saved.

00:15:15.110 --> 00:15:15.120
I

00:15:21.079 --> 00:15:24.710
want to

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:26.949
encourage you all to believe

00:15:26.959 --> 00:15:29.710
God for the big things: speak to your

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:31.710
mountains, speak to the storms,

00:15:31.720 --> 00:15:34.110
speak to your finances.

00:15:36.240 --> 00:15:39.350
Believe for the

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:40.829
impossible, because

00:15:40.839 --> 00:15:42.790
all things are possible to him

00:15:42.790 --> 00:15:42.800
who

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:45.309
believes.

00:15:53.800 --> 00:15:56.350
Father, I thank

00:15:56.360 --> 00:15:57.910
You

00:15:57.920 --> 00:16:01.870
for every single person

00:16:01.880 --> 00:16:03.749
here. We have a mighty

00:16:03.759 --> 00:16:07.309
moving army. We thank

00:16:07.319 --> 00:16:08.870
You that

00:16:08.870 --> 00:16:08.880
we have

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:11.710
authority over storms

00:16:11.710 --> 00:16:11.720
and

00:16:11.720 --> 00:16:14.189
rain. We call forth an

00:16:14.189 --> 00:16:14.199
abundant harvest of

00:16:14.199 --> 00:16:17.389
rain

00:16:21.759 --> 00:16:24.790
over drought

00:16:32.920 --> 00:16:36.350
areas.

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:39.189
We call forth finances

00:16:39.199 --> 00:16:41.910
and

00:16:41.920 --> 00:16:43.670
thank You that

00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:43.680
You

00:16:43.680 --> 00:16:46.629
supply all our needs

00:16:46.639 --> 00:16:49.030
according to Your riches in glory.

00:16:51.759 --> 00:16:54.509
We call people healed.

00:16:56.519 --> 00:16:58.990
Jesus, You took

00:16:58.990 --> 00:16:59.000
it

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:01.069
all on the cross for us so we don't

00:17:01.079 --> 00:17:03.629
have to be sick.

00:17:05.360 --> 00:17:08.549
We

00:17:08.559 --> 00:17:11.990
call our bodies well and whole. We call

00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:31.990
marriages

00:17:32.000 --> 00:17:34.990
restored. Speak to

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:38.870
your marriage: 'My marriage is good; my

00:17:38.880 --> 00:17:41.310
marriage is awesome

00:17:41.310 --> 00:17:41.320
and

00:17:41.320 --> 00:17:45.070
full of love

00:17:45.070 --> 00:17:45.080
and

00:17:45.080 --> 00:17:48.750
joy.'We

00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:51.430
will not have a divorce or corruption in

00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:53.510
this house.

00:18:07.880 --> 00:18:10.669
We bless our

00:18:10.679 --> 00:18:12.909
children that they'll be

00:18:12.919 --> 00:18:14.789
prosperous and not struggle.

00:18:18.640 --> 00:18:22.110
Thank

00:18:22.120 --> 00:18:24.149
You, Lord, that You raise them up.

00:18:27.799 --> 00:18:30.270
It's

00:18:30.280 --> 00:18:31.870
part of my covenant rights to have

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:34.029
children that worship You.

00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:38.950
If my children go wayward, You'll bring

00:18:38.960 --> 00:18:41.470
them back.

00:18:41.480 --> 00:18:43.909
You'll leave the ninety-nine to go after the

00:18:43.919 --> 00:18:47.310
one.

00:18:56.720 --> 00:19:00.310
You have power and

00:19:00.320 --> 00:19:04.470
authority. Read Ephesians over and over

00:19:04.480 --> 00:19:07.510
again and get that

00:19:07.520 --> 00:19:10.470
word deep inside of you. If you

00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:12.310
say you don't hear God, He

00:19:12.310 --> 00:19:12.320
is

00:19:12.320 --> 00:19:15.549
speaking all the time

00:19:15.559 --> 00:19:18.029
through

00:19:18.039 --> 00:19:20.590
the Bible. Pick it

00:19:20.600 --> 00:19:22.430
up and read it.

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:36.149
His mercies are new every

00:19:36.159 --> 00:19:39.590
morning.

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:54.470
I

00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:57.029
hope this video blessed you.

00:19:57.039 --> 00:19:58.710
Know that you

00:19:58.710 --> 00:19:58.720
have that

00:19:58.720 --> 00:20:01.029
authority.

00:20:06.080 --> 00:20:07.750
The devil has no authority to

00:20:07.760 --> 00:20:11.430
torment you.

00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:13.789
You

00:20:13.799 --> 00:20:16.950
tell him, 'Thus far and no

00:20:24.029 --> 00:20:24.039
further.'You've

00:20:34.159 --> 00:20:36.710
got to talk to him like a dog

00:20:36.720 --> 00:20:39.750
because he's a dog. God is good and He's

00:20:39.760 --> 00:20:41.390
faithful.

00:20:50.280 --> 00:20:52.789
Put a

00:20:52.799 --> 00:20:55.630
smile on your face and a song in your

00:20:55.640 --> 00:20:58.950
heart. Jesus loves you, and we

00:20:58.960 --> 00:21:01.270
love you.

00:21:01.280 --> 00:21:03.230
Have a blessed day.

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:06.400
Bye-bye.

